  <summary date="2022-10-17T17:03:18Z" status="Introduced in House">Russia is a State Sponsor of Terrorism Act

This bill designates Russia as a state sponsor of terrorism. (A country with this designation is subject to certain restrictions, including a ban on receiving U.S. defense exports and limits on receiving U.S. foreign assistance.)</summary>
